"instalable: **[build-system]** y **[project]**. La tabla **[project]** "
"almacena los metadatos de su paquete."

#: ../../package-structure-code/pyproject-toml-python-package-metadata.md:17
msgid ""
"There are only two _required_ fields in the **[project]** table: "
"**name=** and **version=**."
msgstr ""
"Existen solo dos campos _requeridos_ en la tabla **[project]**: **name=**"
